# Docs App Guidelines

## UI & Styling
- Implement responsive design with Tailwind CSS; use a mobile-first approach.
- Prefer utility classes over custom CSS


## Framework Guidelines
- Use Next.js App Router conventions
- Place page components in appropriate route segments
- Follow the fumadocs documentation structure
- Keep layouts and pages separate in the app directory

## Component Structure
- Place reusable components in `src/components`
- Use TypeScript for all components (.tsx)
- Follow the fumadocs component patterns for documentation
- Implement responsive design using Tailwind breakpoints

## Documentation
- Follow the fumadocs markdown conventions
- Use MDX for documentation pages
- Keep documentation organized by categories
- Include code examples where appropriate 